cation to distinct robot perception applications,\nincluding robust pose graph optimization, and object-based mapping and\nlocalization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Apr 2022 19:31:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jun 2022 20:21:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2022 19:08:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-21"}
