ered fermions, new high-statistics computations at\nlattice spacings smaller than $0.06$ fm are indispensable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2022 12:25:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 May 2022 09:59:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-05"}
