hifts of conduction band and\nvalence band due to EPI. The present study reveals the phase stability of SnS\nalong with the comparative study of thermal effect on EPI of SnS and SnSe.\nFurther, the possibility of temperature induced topological phase transition\nprovides one of important behaviour to apply these two materials for device\nmaking application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2022 13:01:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
